<item>
            <title>[PIG-3178] Print a stacktrace when ExecutableManager hits an OOM</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3178</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When looking at user&apos;s pig streaming failing with OOM, it only showed&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2013-02-09 03:35:08,694 ERROR &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;Thread-14&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
org.apache.pig.impl.streaming.ExecutableManager: java.lang.OutOfMemoryError:&lt;br/&gt;
Java heap space&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It would have been nice if it also showed the stack trace.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
